# Conventions live in AGENTS.md

All project conventions and path-scoped rules live in `AGENTS.md` files (model-agnostic).

- Root: the repo-root `AGENTS.md`.
- Path-scoped: the `AGENTS.md` in — or nearest above — the directory you are editing (e.g. `apis/AGENTS.md`, `apps/AGENTS.md`, `apps/<app>/AGENTS.md`, `workers/AGENTS.md`, `infrastructure/AGENTS.md`).

Read the relevant `AGENTS.md` before modifying files in a directory.
